title: Summary - Hurricane Tammy (AT5/AL202023)
author: nhcwebmaster@noaa.gov (NHC Webmaster)
summary:
...TAMMY EXPECTED TO BECOME A POWERFUL FRONTAL LOW SOON...
 As of 11:00 PM AST Wed Oct 25
 the center of Tammy was located near 29.9, -57.8
 with movement NNE at 20 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 973 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 90 mph.
